About Me

Hi! My name is Ryan. I graduated from Northwestern Coding Bootcamp and I'm eager to chase my passion in the tech industry. I grew up on Long Island. I lived in Chicago for 4 years, where I obtained my coding bootcamp certificate. The reason I decided to pursue a career in web development is my eagerness to create and further both my professional and personal growth in the ever growing world of tech.
